        <updateDate>2010-03-29T16:18:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Distracted Flying Act - Directs the Secretary of Transportation to initiate a rulemaking for regulations prohibiting, except for operational, emergency safety-related, or employment- related communications, commercial flight crew members from using personal wireless communications devices or laptop computers while on duty on the flight deck of an aircraft that is in operation.</p> <p>Subjects persons to certain penalties for violations of the requirements of this Act.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
